In the MRT.
A boy offering a seat for a lady carrying a baby.
An old man looking on and looking very pleased with the boy’s action.
Another person sitting next to him (old man) points a sign as good to the boy. 
An adult is looking at them angrily. 
A boy is eating a sandwich.
Another adult commuter is telling him to stop and pointing to the ‘no eating’ sign.
Other commuters are reading , listening to music quietly.